ce direct at 464 7357  Repair Maintenance Request Name of Requestor    Email Address    Phone    Where is support needed  Facility Name    Facility Address    Level of Facility    Room Number    Building Coordinator    Building Coordinator extension  Send a copy of this request to    EMERGENCY  PLEASE CALL 464 7357  Repair Maintenance Description    Supply Department  For shipping inquiries  please call 464 7121 Surplus Items  The owning department must contact the Surplus Property Officer in the Purchasing Office  This is done by completing a Disposition of Equipment Form  The Surplus Property Officer will notify the Supply Department of the Physical Plant  If the equipment is being transferred between departments  please complete a Transfer Replacement Form and forward it directly to the Comptroller s Office  Key Request  Please read General Order 56 and complete form  Once form is completed  submit your request  The original must be turned in to the Physical Plant   You will be notified when your key may be picked up at the Physical Plant  Name Door Plate  Please call Armory at 464 7305  When the requested plate has been received submit a repair maintenance request for installation  Please identify any requests not listed above        VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 